    {"zh_des": "通过多模式大语言模型指导基于指令的图像编辑此报告此报告包含通过多模式大语言模型(ICLR‘24 Spotlight)指导基于指令的图像编辑的代码MGIE是\n“基于多模式大语言模型的指导式图像编辑”\n傅资瑞、胡文泽、杜宪志、王威廉、杨银飞、哲干\n在2024国际学习表征会议(ICLR)上，基于指令的图像编辑通过自然命令提高了图像处理的可控性和灵活性，而不需要复杂的描述或区域掩模", "url": "https://github.com/apple/ml-mgie", "name": "apple /ml-mgie", "description": "Guiding Instruction-based Image Editing via Multimodal Large Language Modelsgit clone this repoThis repo contains the code for Guiding Instruction-based Image Editing via Multimodal Large Language Models (ICLR'24 Spotlight)MGIE is an implementation of \n\"Guiding Instruction-based Image Editing via Multimodal Large Language Models\" \nTsu-Jui Fu, Wenze Hu, Xianzhi Du, William Yang Wang, Yinfei Yang, and Zhe Gan \nin International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR) 2024Instruction-based image editing improves the controllability and flexibility of image manipulation via natural commands without elaborate descriptions or regional masks", "stars": "3,148", "forks": "214", "language": "Python", "stars_today": "2,682 stars this week"}
